    <item>
      <title>法尼·威利斯为特朗普丑闻案件聘请的律师辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/fani-willis-defends-attorney-hired-for-trump-case-amid-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，陷入困境的富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯(Fani Willis)在教堂讲坛上打破沉默，对一份爆炸性的法庭文件称她与一名特别律师有恋爱关系，她聘请了一名特别律师来帮助领导对唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)干涉选举的起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/fani-willis-defends-attorney-hired-for-trump-case-amid-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 22:14:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱荷华州共和党主席预测党团会议投票率“强劲”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/iowa-republican-chairman-predicts-robust-caucus-turnout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱荷华州共和党主席杰夫·考夫曼表示，周一晚间共和党党团会议的高投票率将巩固爱荷华州作为该党总统提名程序启动的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/iowa-republican-chairman-predicts-robust-caucus-turnout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 21:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
